Developing this Commodity Management model across all categories**secondary packaging, primary packaging, indirect procurement, API & excipients, and technical purchases**allows the group to:

- Strengthen supply continuity and reduce operational disruptions  
- Ensure full regulatory compliance across all suppliers  
- Drive cost optimization without compromising quality or safety  
- Promote innovation through strategic supplier partnerships  
- Harmonize procurement practices across sites and business units  

Ultimately, Commodity Managers help build a **resilient, compliant, and efficient supply chain**, contributing directly to product availability, patient safety, and the long-term competitiveness of the group.

